    "subtype": "weapon",
    "text": "A fighting oar is a sturdy boat oar, typically made of wood, whose haft and blades are reinforced for use in combat. A fighting oar adds its item bonus from weapon potency runes (if any) as an item bonus on Piloting Lore and Sailing Lore checks made to pilot a rowed vehicle (for more information on vehicles, see here).",
